text: pitabrakd nasa yeung ban bangheanh nouv karottuolkhosatrauv tow aoy mekh cheachraen chean ning phendei haeyning phnom . te puokvea ban bdeseth minoprom ttuol yk vea laey . haey puokvea khlach min ach anouvotd tam ban . haey mnoussa lok kaban ttuol yk vea . pitabrakd nasa ke( mnoussa lok) kuchea anak bampean da lngongkhlaw bamphot
